<h1>SorceryDB Integration</h1>
<p>This page doesn't include the usual setup of js and css files of other SorceryDB pages. Instead, it includes only the files that some external page may want to include to add some features.</p>
<h2>Card Tooltip</h2>
<h3>Setup</h3>
<ul>
<li>include the following CSS files
  <ol>
    <li><tt>https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/qtip2/2.1.1/jquery.qtip.css</tt></li>
    <li><tt>https://sorcerydb.com/netrunnerfont.css</tt></li>
  </ol>
</li>
<li>include the following javscript in your &lt;head&gt; section:
<pre>
  &lt;script src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.0/jquery.min.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
  &lt;script src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/qtip2/2.1.1/jquery.qtip.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
  &lt;script src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/taffydb/2.7.2/taffy-min.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
  &lt;script src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/underscore.js/1.9.1/underscore-min.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
  &lt;script src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/forerunnerdb/1.3.867/fdb-all.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
  &lt;script&gt;
    var NRDB = {};
  &lt;/script&gt;
  &lt;script src="/js/nrdb.tip.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
  &lt;script src="/js/nrdb.data.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
  &lt;script src="/js/nrdb.format.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
  &lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;$.noConflict();&lt;/script&gt;
</pre>
<li>add links pointing to SorceryDB pages, like <a href="https://sorcerydb.com/en/card/01001">Noise: Hacker Extraordinaire</a> or <a href="https://sorcerydb.com/en/card/01041">The Toolbox</a> or <a href="https://sorcerydb.com/en/card/25086">Fetal AI</a></li>
</ul>
<h3>JS encapsulation</h3>
<p>All the code from <tt>nrdb.*.js</tt> lives in the NRDB namespace and uses jQuery in noConflict mode (like this page).</p>
<h3>CSS Styling</h3>
<p>Execute <tt>NRDB.tip.set_hide_event('unfocus')</tt> in the js console to have the tooltips stay on the screen. That should help you style them.</p>
<b>Warning:</b> <tt>style.css</tt> adds styling to all <tt>.icon</tt> elements.
<ul>
<li>the tooltip is <tt>div.qtip-nrdb</tt></li>
<li>the content is <tt>div.qtip-content</tt></li>
<li>the title is <tt>h4</tt></li>
<li>the line of info under the title is <tt>p.card-info</tt></li>
<li>the type in the info line is <tt>span.card-type</tt></li>
<li>the subtype in the info line is <tt>span.card-keywords</tt></li>
<li>the rest of the info line is <tt>span.card-prop</tt></li>
<li>the text of the card is <tt>div.card-text</tt></li>
<li>each line of text of the card is <tt>p</tt></li>
<li>the last line with influence and faction is <tt>p.card-faction</tt></li>
</ul>
<pre>
div.qtip-nrdb
  div.qtip-content
    h4
    p.card-info
      span.card-type
      span.card-keywords
      span.card-prop
    div.card-text
      p
      p
      p
    p.card-faction
</pre>
</body>
